{"tid":2433901,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律政司突放棄覆核四被告保釋 林景楠劉偉聰楊雪盈呂智恆可獲釋","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T07:42:36.000Z","uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0021e60ff4199492dde6c2131ab2811a05764468","tid":2433901,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"47名參與民主派初選的人士被警方控以串謀顛覆國家政權罪，其中15人昨晚獲國安法指定法官、總裁判官蘇惠德批准保釋，惟律政司隨即引用《刑事訴訟程序條例》第9H條，申請覆核保釋決定，按照法例15人須繼續還柙，等候帶上法庭。律政司突今突然放棄追擊四人，包括林景楠、劉偉聰、楊雪盈及呂智恆，四人將被帶到西九龍裁判法院，由蘇官處理保釋事宜。<br />\n<br />\n至於另外的11名被告，則將於明早於高等法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/DAOMLYQIIZD3RECSYPOHTEV554/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FDAOMLYQIIZD3RECSYPOHTEV554%2F&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c9dff78a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210305%2FDAOMLYQIIZD3RECSYPOHTEV554%2F&h=57986c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210305/DAOMLYQIIZD3RECSYPOHTEV554/</a>"},{"pid":"8eb94d1d122056c56042438e478274b99057d81a","tid":2433901,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"阿布泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n西太后<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劉大狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}